    {
        "id":"bogsten_def_evil_0_0",
        "message":"Can I dare to bother you some more ?",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"Of course. Tell me.",
                "nextPhraseID":"bogsten_def_evil_0_1"
            },
            {
                "text":"You're getting on my nerves now. What's it all about this time ?",
                "nextPhraseID":"bogsten_def_evil_0_1"
            },
            {
                "text":"No way ! You've bored me more than enough !",
                "nextPhraseID":"X"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"bogsten_def_evil_0_1",
        "message":"I feel way better but I can't go back to work. The evil forces still lurks down there.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"N",
                "nextPhraseID":"bogsten_def_evil_0_2"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"bogsten_def_evil_0_2",
        "message":"I remember my father warned me about this kind of thing before passing away, but I was just a kid and I forgot his advices on how to deal with it.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"Don't worry. I deal with evil every day. Whatever lurks down there, I can handle it.",
                "nextPhraseID":"bogsten_def_evil_0_3"
            },
            {
                "text":"How can you forget something that important ! I guess I have no choice but to go.",
                "nextPhraseID":"bogsten_def_evil_0_3"
            },
            {
                "text":"Stupid old man. You really think I'm here to clean up your own mess !",
                "nextPhraseID":"X"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"bogsten_def_evil_0_3",
        "message":"Thank you boy. Good luck. Take this necklace with you. I remember my father told me to take it with me when going down there.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"N",
                "nextPhraseID":"X"
            }
        ],
