    {
        "id":"bogsten_def_evil_1_0",
        "message":"Have you finally defeated the evil ?",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"Yes, but it may not be definitive. A sorcerer named Zuul'khan was the source of this. He said something about your ancestors petrifying him with an ancient staff.",
                "nextPhraseID":"bogsten_def_evil_1_1",
                "requires":[
                    {
                        "requireType":"questProgress",
                        "requireID":"bogsten",
                        "value":90
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text":"Stupid old fool. You are the cause, and I am the solution",
                "nextPhraseID":"F",
                "requires":[
                    {
                        "requireType":"questProgress",
                        "requireID":"bogsten",
                        "value":115
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text":"No, not yet.",
                "nextPhraseID":"X"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"bogsten_def_evil_1_1",
        "message":"I remember now ! This was my father's staff. I had to use it while chanting my family's secret incantation in the cave ! How could I have been so careless ?",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"N",
                "nextPhraseID":"bogsten_def_evil_1_2"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"bogsten_def_evil_1_2",
        "message":"Thank you boy. I have not much to offer but my gratitude.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"N",
                "nextPhraseID":"bogsten_def_evil_1_3"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"bogsten_def_evil_1_3",
        "message":"Take this bag of rare mushrooms. I'm sure PM could come up with a good recipe for you.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"Thank you. I'm glad I could help.",
                "nextPhraseID":"bogsten_def_evil_2_0"
