    {
        "id":"zuul_khan_start_0",
        "message":"Who dares to bring violence before me ?",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"Who are you ?",
                "nextPhraseID":"zuul_khan_start_1"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"zuul_khan_start_1",
        "message":"I am the great Zuul'khan. Archmancer of the underground. Master of the Fungis and commander to all that crawls.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"I will save Bogsten from your evil deeds !",
                "nextPhraseID":"zuul_khan_start_2"
            },
            {
                "text":"I'll have to thank Bogsten. This sounds like a fun fight.",
                "nextPhraseID":"zuul_khan_start_2"
            },
            {
                "text":"Please. I will crawl before you. Don't hurt me.",
                "nextPhraseID":"X"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"zuul_khan_start_2",
        "message":"That fool Bogsten ? He sent you here ? Let me tell you a story then.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"N",
                "nextPhraseID":"zuul_khan_start_3"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"zuul_khan_start_3",
        "message":"More than a century ago, I found the way to command the crawling species of the underground and to bend the Fungi to my will. I choose this place to practice my arts and prepare an army of Fungis.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"N",
                "nextPhraseID":"zuul_khan_start_4"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"zuul_khan_start_4",
        "message":"Not long after, Bogsten's grand-grand-grand-father, Bogmer, decided to petrify me using some ancient magical staff and used the remains of the Fungi he slained to create a yet unkown but powerful species of mushroom.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"N",
                "nextPhraseID":"zuul_khan_start_5"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"zuul_khan_start_5",
        "message":"I couldn't do anything but watch him abuse the Fungi in this disgusting way.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"N",
                "nextPhraseID":"zuul_khan_start_6"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"zuul_khan_start_6",
        "message":"But his spell was not strong enough to keep me petrified forever, so every 20 years, Bogmer and his descendants came here with that staff to restore the spell's power.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"N",
                "nextPhraseID":"zuul_khan_start_7"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"zuul_khan_start_7",
        "message":"I don't know why, but Bogsten never did so, and I finally regained my former strength. My army of Fungi can now be reformed, and I will start my revenge by slaying Bogsten and all of his family.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"N",
                "nextPhraseID":"zuul_khan_start_8"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"zuul_khan_start_8",
        "message":"Now that you know the whole story, maybe you can help me. Go slain that fool Bogsten and bring me back the staff. I will reward you with a great present no other man could ever offer you.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"I will reward your throat with my sword !",
                "nextPhraseID":"zuul_khan_def_evil_1_0"
            },
            {
                "text":"I will never betray old Bogsten. Prepare to die !",
                "nextPhraseID":"zuul_khan_def_evil_1_0"
            },
            {
                "text":"That doesn't sound too bad.",
                "nextPhraseID":"zuul_khan_start_9"
            }
        ],
        "rewards":[
